data.description: Nestled in the lovely neighborhood of Miller Ranch, this immaculate 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style. With a secondary bedroom and bathroom conveniently situated on the first level, this home provides flexible living options for guests, family members, or even a home office.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a freshly painted interior and brand new carpeting throughout, creating a welcoming atmosphere that invites you to unwind and make yourself at home.    The spacious layout includes two distinct living areas - one upstairs and one downstairs, providing ample space for both relaxation and entertainment. Whether you're hosting gatherings with loved ones or simply enjoying a quiet evening in, there's a perfect spot for every occasion.    The well-appointed kitchen has modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a breakfast bar, making meal preparation a breeze. Adjacent to the kitchen, you'll find a cozy dining area, perfect for enjoying delicious meals with family and friends.    Upstairs, the primary suite awaits, complete with a luxurious en-suite bathroom and plenty of closet space for all your storage needs. Three additional bedrooms offer comfort and privacy for every member of the household, while two more full bathrooms ensure convenience and functionality.    Outside, the spacious backyard provides endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment, whether you're gardening, grilling, or simply soaking up the sunshine.  Your four-legged family members will enjoy their very own space in the fenced-in dog run with shade.    Located in close proximity to JBSA/Fort Sam Houston, Brooke Army Medical Center, and Randolph Air Force Base, this home offers unparalleled convenience for military personnel and their families. Miller Ranch is also conveniently located right across the street from Wagner High School.  Enjoy easy access to shopping, dining, recreation, and more, ensuring that everything you need is always within reach.
